
Terminal Definition:
The Terminal is a way to input data, and showing or printing data from the computer.

Major Difference Between Git and GitHub:
The major difference between Git and GitHub is that Git  is an open source tool
people can install locally on your computer while GitHub  is an online service.

Why We Use GitHub:
We use GitHub to show other developers our work. It is also easier to work with
someone through a GitHub repository. GitHub may also run as a host for your HTML
 website. 
